<i>♪ We are the Crystal Gems ♪</i>

00:04.540 --> 00:07.070
<i>♪ we'll always save the day ♪</i>

00:07.130 --> 00:09.200
<i>♪ and if you think we can't ♪</i>

00:09.200 --> 00:12.070
<i>♪ we'll always find a way ♪</i>

00:12.070 --> 00:15.970
<i>- ♪ that's why the people ♪
- ♪ of this world ♪</i>

00:15.970 --> 00:18.340
<i>- ♪ believe in... ♪
- ♪ Garnet ♪</i>

00:18.340 --> 00:21.140
<i>- ♪ Amethyst ♪
- ♪ and Pearl ♪</i>

00:21.150 --> 00:22.810
<i>♪ And Steven! ♪</i>

00:25.880 --> 00:27.570
<b>1x37 - "Alone Together" </b>

00:27.570 --> 00:29.200
<i><font color="cyan">sync & correction by f1nc0
